      <div type="translation">
        <p n="1"> Success! Homage to the Bhagavant, the Perfect Buddha, who is
					ensconced in the excellent relic [or: element (<hi rend="italic">i.e.</hi>, <foreign xml:lang="san-Latn">nirvāṇadhātu</foreign>)]! </p>
        <p n="1-3"> At the Great Shrine, ...
					favored by Mahāsena who has (Virūpākṣa) as his lord,
					(sacrificer of) the Agnihotra, the Agniṣṭoma, the Vājapeya
					(and the Aśvamedha), (giver of hundreds of thousands of cows
					and hundreds of) thousands of plows (of land)… </p>
      </div>
